text: Patrick Nys (born 25 January 1969) is a Belgian former football goalkeeper who lasted played for F.C. Brussels. As of the summer of 2010, he is a goalkeeper coach with Antwerp FC. == Honours == * Gençlerbirliği **Turkish Cup (1): 2001 ==References== Category:Belgian footballers Category:Association football goalkeepers Category:Gençlerbirliği S.K. footballers Category:R.W.D.M.
